==============================================================================
Desired Performance Data
==============================================================================

  1. Tput vs. G (traffic load)
  2. PER vs. SINR (for n=1,2,3... colliders)

==============================================================================
Experiments
==============================================================================
  1. awgn.hydra.mcs{0,3,6}
     * ALOHA using Hydra PHY with specified MCS
     * CM-A (no fading)
  2. awgn.model.mcs{0,3,6} - ALOHA using WiNS model with specified MCS
     * ALOHA using WiNS model with specified MCS
     * CM-A (no fading)
  3. cmd.hydra.mcs{0,3,6}
     * ALOHA using Hydra PHY with specified MCS
     * CM-D (disable time-selective fading)

==============================================================================
Additional Directories
==============================================================================
  * rawdata/ -raw trace files
  * parsedata/ - parsed data files (unformatted)
  * paperdata/ - formatted data used to create graphs in papers

